unittitle_ssm: Kings County Clerk bonds of administration
abstract_ssm: This collection contains 12 bound volumes of Kings County Clerk's office bonds of administration, with registers of property transactions in the county. Each volume's entries span approximately 2 months, noting the principles, dates, and locations of each transaction. Each volume also contains an index of names.
